      "description": "Hey everyone! I am so excited to put my absolute pride and joy up for sale. This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014it looks and feels exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and has been meticulously cared for since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
