    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-tier condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings and VANOS system have been professionally addressed. The chassis is laser-straight with original bushings and a pristine undercarriage. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. A mechanically superior specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "2021 Luxury Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No mechanical issues. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
