    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior is finished in its original factory paint, which retains a deep, mirror-like luster entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin still carries a hint of that 'new car' scent; the premium leather seats are supple and devoid of bolster wear, while the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since new. Mechanically, this vehicle is indistinguishable from a showroom model. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a thick binder of service records. From the crisp engagement of the transmission to the silent operation of every electronic feature and switch, it performs flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example that satisfies the most rigorous inspection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
